                  <summary><p>The <title xml:lang="ta">Akarāti Nikaṇṭu</title>, entitled here <title xml:lang="ta">Citampara Akarāti Nikaṇṭu</title> (U1). 3368 <foreign xml:lang="ta">cūttiram</foreign>s.</p>
<p>See <title>Madras Tamil Lexicon</title>, s.v.: <quote rend="block">அகராதிநிகண்டு akarāti-nikaṇtu , n.  id. +. Name of a  thesaurus in verse, as giving the words in alphabetical order, by Citampara-rēvaṇa-cittar, A.D. 1594; ஒரு நிகண்டு நூல்.</quote></p> 

<p>Description based on the examination of the original manuscript (February 2023).</p>
<p>Dimensions assessed at the time of examination.</p>          </summary>
                  
